author: Reuters
title: DIARY - Today in Washington - Aug 25
text:
ALL TIMES IN EDT/GMT
0900/1300: The Federal Housing Finance Agency issues House Price Index for June.
1000/1400: The Commerce Dept. issues Single-Family Home Sales for July.
1130/1530.: The Treasury Dept. holds weekly sale of 4-week bills.
1300/1700: The Treasury Dept. sells 2-year notes.
1630/2030: The American Petroleum Institute issues weekly national petroleum report.
